ares javax.servlet:servlet-api as a provided dependency managed by jackrabbit-parent at version 2.3; public classes such as WebdavRequestImpl, DavServletRequest, DavServletResponse, InputContextImpl, OutputContextImpl, and AbstractWebdavServlet reference javax.servlet APIs.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No Docker image, external WebDAV server, environment variable, or system property is indicated. Prefer in-memory tests of headers, XML/properties, reports, methods, locator factories, and servlet-facing adapters using mocks/proxies or lightweight stubs for request/response objects rather than starting a container.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Because the servlet API is provided rather than transitive, scaffold-only dependency resolution may compile only non-servlet tests and miss a major part of normal server-side usage.\",\n    \"The existing native-image run failure appears to be in pure locator behavior, so the servlet dependency is setup for coverage reachability, not necessarily the direct fix for the reported native runtime assertion failures.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ea829d8f98b67a8016a42a30a18a081959e7bd77053410599\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1288, "output": 870, "cacheRead": 22016, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 24174, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782752000011, "responseId": "resp_0ea829d8f98b67a8016a42a3008d488195bac98a785c42cb4b"}}
